{"word":"τρίμετρος","slug":"τρίμετρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n105040\" key=\"tri/metros\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">τρίμετρος</orth> <pron extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pron\">[ῐ]</pron>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, of verses, <sense id=\"n105040.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">consisting of three</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μέτρα;</foreign> i. e. in iambics, trochaics, and anapaestics, of three <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">συζυγίαι</foreign> (of two feet each); but in dactylics, etc., of three single feet: hence the iambic verse of six feet is called by the Greeks <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἴαμβος τρίμετρος,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.12</biblScope> </bibl>; so <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τόνος τ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">trimeter</tr_> verse, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:174\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">174</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔπη τ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:810e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">810e</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τρίμετρον, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg003.perseus-grc1:642\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nu.\">Nu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">642</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg034.perseus-grc1:1447b:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Po.\">Po.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1447b11</biblScope> </bibl> (pl.). </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n105040.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τρίμετρος, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>,</foreign> a measure of capacity for oil, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.422</biblScope> </bibl> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\"> iii 44</biblScope> </bibl> (<placeName TEIform=\"placeName\">Tauromenium</placeName>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}